t;hkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>I\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>J-L\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/line\"><code>&lt;line&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/linearGradient\"><code>&lt;linearGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>M\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/metadata\"><code>&lt;metadata&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mpath\"><code>&lt;mpath&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>N-P\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>Q-R\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/radialGradient\"><code>&lt;radialGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>S\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section>\n<p>The <strong><code>word-spacing</code></strong> attribute specifies spacing behavior between words.</p>\n<p>If a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a> is provided without a unit identifier (e.g. an unqualified number such as 128), the browser processes the &lt;length&gt; as a width value in the current user coordinate system.</p>\n<p>If a &lt;length&gt; is provided with one of the unit identifiers (e.g. .25em or 1%), then the browser converts the &lt;length&gt; into a corresponding value in the current user coordinate system.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> As a presentation attribute, <code>word-spacing</code> can be used as a CSS property. See the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/word-spacing\"><code>css word-spacing</code></a> property for more information.</p>\n</div>\n<p>You can use this attribute with the following SVG elements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/altGlyph\"><code>&lt;altGlyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css hidden notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">html,\nbody,\nsvg</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 250 50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>text</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>20<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">word-spacing</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Bigger spacing between words<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>text</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>40<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">word-spacing</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>-0.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Smaller spacing between words<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"250\" height=\"100\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/word-spacing/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_notes","title":"Usage notes","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n      <td><code>normal</code> | <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Default values</th>\n      <td><code>normal</code></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>For a description of the values, please refer to the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/letter-spacing#values\">CSS <code>letter-spacing</code></a> property.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-text/#word-spacing-property","title":"CSS Text Module Level 3"}],"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.word-spacing"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.word-spacing","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/word-spacing/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/word-spacing\"><code>css word-spacing</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Usage notes","id":"usage_notes"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The word-spacing attribute specifies spacing behavior between words.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-13T09:59:48.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/svg/attribute/word-spacing","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/svg/attribute/word-spacing/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/0d3